### API WatchMeGym - Testes de Bioimpedâncias
### Use a extensão REST Client do VS Code para executar estes testes

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@userId = 8c7e355a-41b8-4373-83cf-6b43ba26c884
@bioimpedanceId = {{createBioimpedance.response.body.bioimpedance.id}}

### 1. Criar Bioimpedância
# @name createBioimpedance
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bioimpedances
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "weight": 75.5,
  "height": 1.75,
  "bmi": 24.65,
  "bmr": 1650.5
}

###

### 2. Listar Todas as Bioimpedâncias
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bioimpedances

###

### 3. Buscar Bioimpedância por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bioimpedances/{{bioimpedanceId}}

###

### 4. Buscar Bioimpedâncias por Usuário
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bioimpedances/user/{{userId}}

###

### 5. Buscar Última Bioimpedância do Usuário
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bioimpedances/user/{{userId}}/latest

###

### 6. Atualizar Bioimpedância
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/bioimpedances/{{bioimpedanceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weight": 76.0,
  "bmi": 24.82
}

###

### 7. Deletar Bioimpedância
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/bioimpedances/{{bioimpedanceId}}

###

